{"tid":1634140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人講?台灣「狂新聞」力撐示威者","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:07:42.000Z","uid":205394,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8993d308fc0c1acba85776a12842785c42585672","tid":1634140,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"狂新聞係台灣網上新聞媒體<br />\n每星期都會整個一至五排名出黎講各國新聞<br />\n多數都係以搞笑為主<br />\n<br />\n今個星期佢地將我地香港既示威新聞排第一位<br />\n而且重好強烈表態支持我地<br />\n最後重播左一段我地示威者咆哮既畫面<br />\n睇到熱血沸騰<br />\n<br />\n睇狂新聞既多數都係台灣既年青人<br />\n佢呢條片一出,台灣文宣戰場真係勝過我地出再多文宣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mv0HVkFZpO8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMv0HVkFZpO8&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=4fc376ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mv0HVkFZpO8</a><br />\n<br />\n一齊訂閱佢同支持佢啦!"},{"pid":"1e209922ee7f116bc1789316a7257a24b64356b9","tid":1634140,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:43:15.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d81241cf7c1aefcac1cc985a8c6c5099d232d139","tid":1634140,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"679e8c3845ee623f9a62e9de24084031238c6453","tid":1634140,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"c907b5a9e0cf9cb358d3972b7d176ace11efa2f1","tid":1634140,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:44:28.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"cd3367e03dbe587b4b38f3ad5ffe7d43cc565717","tid":1634140,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"afbcf8ee901cd8cec16adb1f97d3d5e71f00a7bb","tid":1634140,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:47:52.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"23435ffa39dc1dc925b954214